## Resolved Decisions

| # | Question | Decision |
|---|----------|----------|
| 1 | Frontend scope | **Backend-only**. User builds client separately. |
| 2 | Auth method | **Email + bcrypt password**. No OAuth for V1. |
| 3 | Media uploads | **Text-only** DMs and Feed for V1. |
| 4 | Rate limiting | **No IP/time rate limiting**. Instead: **Exact-Duplicate Text Filter** in `client.go` — track last sent message, silently drop exact repeats. |
